You are infinite
a starscape
a never-ending sea of unfulfilled potential
you are an adventure
unspoiled
a discovery
you are deep difficult dark hard to navigate
dangerous
but hide your treasures

you hide your treasures well

plain, to the naked eye unvarnished
infinite, a starscape
a never-ending sea

You are infinite,
an adventure,
unspoiled,
a discovery -
you are deep difficult dark hard to navigate -
dangerous,
you hide your treasures well -
plain, to the naked eye unvarnished,
infinite, a starscape,
a never-ending sea.
